inquiries.query:
/*
In the job_postings_fact table only get jobs that have an average yearly salary less  than $11,0000.
Also get the job_id, job_title_short, job_location, job_via, and salary_year_avg columns

*/

SELECT
	job_id,
    job_title_short,
    job_location,
    job_via,
    salary_year_avg
	
FROM 
	job_postings_fact
where
	salary_year_avg < 110000;
